{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/circus-politicus-board-game-seru-bertema-politik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Circus Politicus: Board Game Seru Bertema Politik","content":"\n<p>Pengembang dan penerbit video game asal Tangerang, Toge Productions hari ini mengumumkan produk terbaru mereka yang berjudul Circus Politicus. Game terbaru ini juga merupakan sepak terjang pertama Toge Productions ke dunia board game setelah eksis sepuluh tahun merilis berbagai game digital untuk PC, konsol, dan smartphone.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53421\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/circus-politicus-board-game-seru-bertema-politik/attachment/01-circus-politicus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-circus-politicus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-circus-politicus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-circus-politicus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-circus-politicus.jpg\" alt=\"Circus Politicus. Sumber: Toge Productions\" class=\"wp-image-53421\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-circus-politicus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Circus Politicus. Sumber: Toge Productions</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Circus Politicus merupakan sebuah permainan kartu bertema parodi politik yang terinspirasi dari kejadian-kejadian yang terjadi selama kampanye politik berlangsung, namun dikembangkan menjadi <em>card game</em> yang seru, penuh dengan elemen strategi, &nbsp;dan disajikan dengan visual ala karikatur kartun yang menarik dan lucu, menambahkan kesan parodi kental ke dalamnya.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53422\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/circus-politicus-board-game-seru-bertema-politik/attachment/02-circus-politicus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-circus-politicus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-circus-politicus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-circus-politicus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-circus-politicus.jpg\" alt=\"Package Circus Politicus. Sumber: Toge Productions\" class=\"wp-image-53422\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-circus-politicus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Package Circus Politicus. Sumber: Toge Productions</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Board game ini menempatkan pemain sebagai manajer tim sukses pasangan kandidat politik. Pemain harus mengatur strategi dan berkonspirasi demi mendapatkan suara terbanyak dan memenangkan agenda politik kandidat mereka. Dengan kondisi politik yang saat ini semakin memanas, permainan ini hadir dengan tujuan untuk mendamaikan teman-teman yang bermusuhan karena mendukung paslon yang berbeda sekaligus menyadarkan masyarakat agar tidak termakan strategi-strategi politik yang dapat memecah belah bangsa.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Terlahir dari ajang Global Game Jam, acara membuat game selama 48 jam yang berlangsung di awal 2017, permainan yang seratus persen dibuat anak bangsa ini akan segera tersedia untuk dibeli pada 25 Maret 2019. Pemesanan Pre-Order dapat dilakukan melalui tautan <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://togeproductions-dot-yamm-track.appspot.com/Redirect?ukey=19t063EqNNYi1ylQMiBde6aenPp2mnxS71_YYgJzGrW8-8112522&amp;key=YAMMID-45314865&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fcircuspoliticustokopedia\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/circuspoliticustokopedia</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Baca Juga: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/first-look-board-game-chips-heroes-uprising/\" target=\"_blank\">First Look Board Game CHIPS: Heroes Uprising</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53423\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/circus-politicus-board-game-seru-bertema-politik/attachment/03-circus-politicus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-circus-politicus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-circus-politicus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-circus-politicus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-circus-politicus.jpg\" alt=\"Kartu para leader. Sumber: Toge Productions\" class=\"wp-image-53423\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-circus-politicus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Kartu para leader. Sumber: Toge Productions</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>“Kami pertama mencoba prototipe dari Circus Politicus sejak dibuat di Global Game Jam dan langsung melihat potensi yang dimilikinya,” jelas Kris Antoni selaku CEO Toge Productions.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>“Sempat ada banyak diskusi tentang tema yang akan diangkat permainan ini, namun setelah melihat aturan bermain yang makin diperbaharui serta menyaksikan ramainya pembicaraan yang terjadi di dunia maya, kami putuskan untuk menjadikan <em>Circus Politicus</em> sebuah game parodi bertema politik. Jadilah sebuah permainan politik tanpa polemik,” tambah Kris.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53424\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/circus-politicus-board-game-seru-bertema-politik/attachment/04-circus-politicus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-circus-politicus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-circus-politicus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-circus-politicus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-circus-politicus.jpg\" alt=\"Kartu yang bisa dimainkan. Sumber: Toge Productions\" class=\"wp-image-53424\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-circus-politicus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Kartu yang bisa dimainkan. Sumber: Toge Productions</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut ini adalah beberapa fitur dari board game ini<em>.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Permainan kartu dengan aturan main simpel yang dikembangkan dengan elemen strategi yang mendalam </li><li>Tema parodi politik yang mengizinkan pemain untuk memilih politisi, mengeluarkan janji-janji, dan menjalankan agenda politis demi memenangkan permainan</li><li>Kesempatan untuk bermain sebagai parodi tokoh-tokoh ternama seperti Jokowo, Prabowi, Donold Trump, Theresa June, Jim Kong Un, dan lainnya</li><li>Puluhan kartu dengan ilustrasi menarik buatan ilustrator asal Jakarta, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://togeproductions-dot-yamm-track.appspot.com/Redirect?ukey=19t063EqNNYi1ylQMiBde6aenPp2mnxS71_YYgJzGrW8-8112522&amp;key=YAMMID-45314865&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwd.willy%2F\" target=\"_blank\">WD Willy</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53425\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/circus-politicus-board-game-seru-bertema-politik/attachment/05-circus-politicus/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-circus-politicus.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-circus-politicus\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-circus-politicus.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-circus-politicus.jpg\" alt=\"Suasana playing area Circus Politicus. Sumber: Toge Productions\" class=\"wp-image-53425\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-circus-politicus.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-circus-politicus-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Suasana playing area Circus Politicus. Sumber: Toge Productions</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Circus Politicus akan segera tersedia untuk dibeli secara online maupun di beberapa toko board game pada 25 Maret 2019. Dapatkan berita terbaru mengenai board game ini melalui akun resmi game ini di <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://togeproductions-dot-yamm-track.appspot.com/Redirect?ukey=19t063EqNNYi1ylQMiBde6aenPp2mnxS71_YYgJzGrW8-8112522&amp;key=YAMMID-45314865&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcircuspoliticus%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://togeproductions-dot-yamm-track.appspot.com/Redirect?ukey=19t063EqNNYi1ylQMiBde6aenPp2mnxS71_YYgJzGrW8-8112522&amp;key=YAMMID-45314865&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcircuspolitic\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>, dan <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://togeproductions-dot-yamm-track.appspot.com/Redirect?ukey=19t063EqNNYi1ylQMiBde6aenPp2mnxS71_YYgJzGrW8-8112522&amp;key=YAMMID-45314865&amp;link=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcircuspoliticus%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a>.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"8904e4e8-e4a3-50d5-aa8c-b00cf8a99ef3"}}}